  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Bim Modeller",
  "description": "<p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>•⁠  ⁠Perform 3D BIM modeling for MEP services, with focus on ACMV, Electrical, Fire Protection, and Plumbing &amp; Sanitary (P&amp;S) systems.  </p>\n<p>•⁠  Modeling for MEP Services (especially Plumbing and Sanitary Service)</p>\n<p>•⁠  ⁠Provide AutoCAD drawings and BIM models to support the project team. </p>\n<p>•⁠ Prepared shop drawing for submission and As-Built Drawings for site inspection. </p>\n<p>•⁠  ⁠Update models based on the latest Engineer’s Instructions (EIs) from consultants.  </p>\n<p>•⁠  ⁠Prepare and submit construction shop drawings, detail drawings, and as-built drawings in compliance with project BIM standards.  </p>\n<p>•⁠  ⁠Develop standard installation details for the company and review them with engineers prior to submission.  </p>\n<p>•⁠  3D Co-ordination &amp; clash detection for MEP service in Revit and Navisworks Manage</p>\n<p>•⁠  ⁠Coordinate with site engineers on detailed drawings, penetration layouts, and additional sketches required by consultants.  </p>\n<p>•⁠  ⁠Manage and submit Combined Services Drawings (CSD) for BIM coordination.  </p>\n<p>•⁠  ⁠Prepare and submit monthly BIM progress reports to the BIM Manager.  </p>\n<p>•⁠  ⁠Maintain accurate records of drawings, reports, and documentation for the project.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Basic Technical Software Skills:</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Microsoft Tool</p>\n<p>- Microsoft World</p>\n<p>- Microsoft Excel</p>\n<p>- Microsoft Power Point</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Drafting Tool </p>\n<p>- Auto CAD</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Modeling Tool </p>\n<p>- Revit (MEP)</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>",
